'''Harry Holm''' is the son of [[Ian Holm]]. His crying can be heard in the [[The Lord of the Rings (1981 radio series)|radio series]] of ''[[The Lord of the Rings]]'', where he is credited as [[Elanor Gardner|Elanor Fairbairns]].
